Ordonez Says CAM Executives’ Compensation Issue Is ‘Scandalous’

-- B y   S h a r o n   S m y t h
-- 
2011-09-30T10:49:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-30/ordonez-says-cam-executives-compensation-issue-is-scandalous-.html
Bank of Spain Governor Miguel Angel
Fernandez Ordonez said the issue of pension payments and other
compensation to board member of CAM exectutives is
“scandalous” during a press conference in  Madrid  today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
